replyContent: There is quite a bit of content, and it is tested on various devices and Android versions.  Please email us using the "Feedback" option, and we can help figure out what is failing on your device.

replyContent: The bug with bookmarks has been resolved.  The request to adjust font size is a much larger change, and is under consideration for future updates.

content: How do I give this 10 Stars? :-)
This is a fantastic app, the only thing missing is a setting to adjust the font size.  Would be 5 stars with that.
Well presented app, great to have all documents in one place, only 4 stars as I think as an Englishmen you have a bit of a cheek including Magna Carta in  a list of USA documents
replyContent: Thanks for the input.  The Magna Carta was added because it is a major foundation document for what the United States was to become.  It was one of the significant historical documents used by the founding fathers as reference, and the ideas encapsulated in the Magna Carta were built upon as a base.

replyContent: Please check out the latest update yesterday.  We have added several new documents, including several of your suggestions.  This app will continue to add documents over time.
